body:
**Improvements**:

* Load `resource-loader` from jCenter.

**Breaking**:

You may need to add `jCenter` to your repositories section. Something like this should work:

```groovy
// Top level build file 
repositories {
    jcenter()

    // May not need this as lazysodium is available in jCenter
    // but jCenter often is slower to update.
    maven {
        url  "https://dl.bintray.com/terl/lazysodium-maven"
    }
}

// Add to dependencies section in app level build file
dependencies {
    implementation "com.goterl.lazycode:lazysodium-java:VERSION_NUMBER"
}
```
